            "title": "爆一爆｜做佐丹奴股東真好 回水15億後再派好息（Louise）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"今次佐丹奴派未期息6.4仙，周大福企業連同自己友袋＄5632萬。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DugeVM0IfY4yiOI2brkpxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-02/375d9000-4f09-11ea-bdcd-0bc90da5f0ad\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">今次<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"佐丹奴\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:佐丹奴;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/佐丹奴\">佐丹奴</a>派未期息6.4仙，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"周大福\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:周大福;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/周大福\">周大福</a>企業連同自己友袋＄5632萬。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">都唔知幾耐冇幫襯過佐丹奴買衫了，不過佐丹奴國際（0709.HK）公佈業績，有粒數字都幾礙眼，其末期派息比率（payout ratio）達到108.5%，</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">派息比率逾100%！</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超過100%，即係派息多過公司賺嘅錢，真係威過賺幾多派幾多嘅房地產信託基金REITs。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">佐丹奴嘅大股東乃是鄭氏家族的周大福企業，表面持有24%權益。但年廿九證監會公佈鄭家旗下的周大福代理人，就涉嫌隱瞞佐丹奴一次行動人士持股達55％，為了息事寧人周大福企業主動獻身向小股東回水＄15億，你話做佐丹奴小股東幾好呢？有水回兼有息派。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6c08ebfb-6c88-44d1-b765-1645f2088690-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今次佐丹奴派未期息6.4仙，周大福企業連同自己友袋＄5632萬，雖然與回水小股東15億相距乃有一大截，但總算幫補一下，未來亦可能長派長有。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">集團揸7億現金</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事關佐丹奴老臣子兼開國功臣劉國權已被踢走，無人阻頭阻勢，由鄭家主持大局就想點都得啦。據知2012年彤叔仍在生時，其財技了得的馬仔莊天龍（Benny Chong） 建議彤叔入股佐丹奴，當時就係睇中公司入面嘅現金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">家陣就可以實現彤叔生前嘅諗法，正如佐丹奴財務總監陳嘉緯公佈業績時，認為公司現金過剩，咪回饋股東囉，希望股東開心咁話。佐丹奴現時坐擁現金有近7億，為咗令股東開心，相信未來佐丹奴會繼續派好息。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%88%86%E4%B8%80%E7%88%86%EF%BD%9C%E5%81%9A%E4%BD%90%E4%B8%B9%E5%A5%B4%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%9F%E5%A5%BD-%E5%9B%9E%E6%B0%B415%E5%84%84%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E6%B4%BE%E5%A5%BD%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%88louise%EF%BC%89-132140985.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-26 21:30:23",
