        },
        {
            "title": "Jefferies Financial、MillerKnoll盤前下跌;Kodiak Sciences飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkT.J6EQ.Cm0QnT5ytAxjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7306L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國股指期貨週四走低,油價重新跳升至每桶100美元上方,儘管有報導稱美國與伊朗之間可能進行和平談判,但中東地區的戰鬥仍在激烈進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間07:36(北京時間19:36),道瓊斯期貨合約下跌351點,跌幅0.8%,標普500期貨下跌53點,跌幅0.8%,納斯達克100期貨下跌230點,跌幅0.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是今日盤前美股主要異動股:</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國礦業股在盤前交易中回落,旅遊股如聯合航空(United Airlines)和達美航空(Delta Air Lines)等航空公司也出現下跌。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">郵輪營運商嘉年華集團(Carnival Corp.)也下跌,分析師此前指出該公司可能面臨燃料價格上漲的風險。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">石油巨頭埃克森美孚(Exxon Mobil)和雪佛龍(Chevron)走高。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jefferies Financial公布的業績未能達到投資者預期,儘管第一季投資銀行業務回報強勁,但對倒閉公司貸款的損失蓋過了這一亮點。股價下跌超過1.8%。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶體晶片股,包括美光科技(Micron)和SanDisk,在谷歌(Google)研究人員提出一種新的壓縮技術後均下跌,該技術可能減少驅動人工智能工具所需的記憶體量。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kodiak Sciences因其針對糖尿病眼部併發症的實驗性治療藥物後期試驗數據而飆升。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">商務旅行平台Navan公布了優於預期的第四季業績,推動股價走高。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Preceigen股價飆升,這家生物製藥公司第一季業績受其治療復發性呼吸道乳頭狀瘤病藥物的強勁表現支撐。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MillerKnoll暴跌,這家辦公家具設計公司公布的第四財季盈利展望令人失望。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
