            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特朗普稱伊朗最好盡快認真起來 否則將沒有回頭路且局面「不會好看」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"特朗普稱伊朗最好盡快認真起來 否則將沒有回頭路且局面「不會好看」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g3Ygn8s0MPn3T7lnfnokww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/6bd00b70-2913-11f1-bb67-3c4398eda335\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普稱伊朗最好盡快認真起來 否則將沒有回頭路且局面「不會好看」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
